  <num>38-402</num>
  <heading>Control of school construction and repairs.</heading>
  <text>The Director of the Department of Consumer and Regulatory Affairs (“Director”) shall have the same authority, control over, and supervision of the construction or repair of a public school building as the Director has of the construction or repair of any privately owned building.</text>
